Human Body (Tell Me Why #101)
By Manorama
English | February 2015 | PDF | 98 pages | 12 mb
scanned to PDF by me.

THE BODY MACHINE
A car that zooms past you looks so simple and smooth. Yet, it is a complex machine with numerous parts. All the parts must work in perfect harmony for the car to run.
It's the same for the human body too, which is often compared to a machine - an amazing machine, more sophisticated, and complex than anything Man has ever made. How its complex parts all work together perfectly, to make our life a meaningful experience is a scientific wonder.
This issue of 'Tell Me Why' helps you explore, this wonderful machine called human body.
